 archipelago\", \"from\": 229, \"to\": 259}, {\"ngram\": \"reinforced police forces\", \"from\": 267, \"to\": 291}, {\"ngram\": \"deadly riots\", \"from\": 305, \"to\": 317}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He pledged that these forces \\\"will stay as long as necessary\\\", even as France prepares for the massive security operation required for the upcoming Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 320, \"to\": 482, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 391, \"end\": 397, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Third_Republic\", \"score\": 0.9378654267000655, \"rank\": 0.045214102709361395, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Third_Republic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Third_Republic\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"these forces\", \"from\": 336, \"to\": 348}, {\"ngram\": \"the massive security operation\", \"from\": 411, \"to\": 441}, {\"ngram\": \"the upcoming Olympic Games\", \"from\": 455, \"to\": 481}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Macron scrapped his previous schedule to personally address the crisis, flying from Paris to New Caledonia.\", \"from\": 484, \"to\": 591, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 484, \"end\": 490, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.518535958461534e-28, \"text\": \"Macron\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\"}, {\"begin\": 568, \"end\": 573, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999998040039, \"rank\": 1.9582816505899406e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 577, \"end\": 590, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Caledonia\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.296996807643611e-29, \"text\": \"New Caledonia\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http