port\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/La_Tontouta_International_Airport\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"ourPrivacy Policy\", \"from\": 2048, \"to\": 2065}, {\"ngram\": \"WW3 fears\", \"from\": 2078, \"to\": 2087}, {\"ngram\": \"clearly' building momentum\", \"from\": 2123, \"to\": 2149}, {\"ngram\": \"embarrassing election poll\", \"from\": 2199, \"to\": 2225}, {\"ngram\": \"siege\", \"from\": 2326, \"to\": 2331}, {\"ngram\": \"his intent\", \"from\": 2394, \"to\": 2404}, {\"ngram\": \"peace\", \"from\": 2416, \"to\": 2421}, {\"ngram\": \"security\", \"from\": 2426, \"to\": 2434}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He also mentioned plans to discuss economic reconstruction and political issues concerning the future of New Caledonia.\", \"from\": 2448, \"to\": 2567, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2553, \"end\": 2566, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Caledonia\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.296996807643611e-29, \"text\": \"New Caledonia\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Caledonia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Caledonia\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"plans\", \"from\": 2466, \"to\": 2471}, {\"ngram\": \"economic reconstruction\", \"from\": 2483, \"to\": 2506}, {\"ngram\": \"political issues\", \"from\": 2511, \"to\": 2527}, {\"ngram\": \"the future\", \"from\": 2539, \"to\": 2549}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We will discuss questions of economic reconstruction, support and rapid response, and the most delicate political questions, as we talk about the future of New Caledonia,\\\" Macron said.\", \"from\": 2569, \"to\": 2754, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2726, \"end\": 2739, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Caledonia\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.296996807643611e-29, \"text\": \"New Caledonia\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Caledonia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Caledonia\"}, {\"begin\": 2742, \"end\": 2748, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resour